			"previous": " At his talk at the 2009 Aspen Ideas Festival Professor Lessig talked about Forbin Problems in a talk entitled Will Technology Change Our Lives 27 and also about his idea that the American public has lost faith in the central institution of their democracy Congress 28 ",
